主要功能

人工智能建模和自动绘图
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down
Translated:
Artificial intelligence modeling and automated drawings
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down

Content: 利用 NX X Essentials 人工智能预测直接建模和自动 2D 图纸生成功能，简化 3D CAD 建模。人工智能预测建模可即时识别设计意图，非常适用于处理 CAD 数据，或快速生成新概念设计并轻松应对更改请求。工装功能简化了刀轨创建，让设计人员可以轻松为数控和其他机床生成并优化路径，充分减少设置时间和复杂性。
Translated: Simplify 3D CAD modeling by using NX X Essentials artificial intelligence prediction direct modeling and automated 2D drawing generation capabilities. Artificial intelligence predictive modeling can instantly recognize design intent, which is very suitable for processing CAD data, or quickly generating new concept designs and easily responding to modification requests. The tooling function simplifies the creation of toolpaths, allowing designers to easily generate and optimize paths for CNC and other machine tools, fully reducing setup time and complexity.

Content:
通过浏览器访问，不限设备
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down
Translated:
Access via browser, regardless of device
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down

Content: CAD 查看和批注功能适用于所有设备，支持在工程导向型三维空间中对模型进行查看、测量和批注。通过该功能，您可以对模型进行缩放、旋转或检查，并添加注释和评论。所有批注和评论在 NX X Essentials 中都完全可追溯并可随时查看，让项目审查全程可见。通过 NX X Essentials 增强现实 (AR)，您可以使用智能设备在真实环境中预览设计效果。通过基于权限的共享和无限制访客访问权限，您可以与团队成员、同事、合作伙伴和客户进行协作。
Translated: CAD viewing and annotation functionality is applicable to all devices, supporting the viewing, measurement and annotation of models in engineering-oriented 3D space. Through this function, you can zoom, rotate or inspect the model, and add annotations and comments. All annotations and comments in NX X Essentials are fully traceable and can be viewed at any time, making the project review process fully visible. Through augmented reality (AR) in NX X Essentials, you can use smart devices to preview design effects in a real environment. Through permission-based sharing and unrestricted access to access rights, you can collaborate with team members, colleagues, partners, and customers.

Content:
计划、执行和跟踪项目和任务
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down
Translated:
Plan, execute and track projects and tasks
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down

Content: 通过 NX X Essentials 任务管理，您可以设置到期日期、优先级和参考项目文件，高效管理和跟踪交付成果。交互式项目仪表板可对项目和工作状态进行实时监控和跟踪。
Translated: With NX X Essentials task management, you can set due dates, priorities, and reference project files, efficiently manage and track deliverables. Interactive project dashboards provide real-time monitoring and tracking of project and work status.

Content: 利用 NX X Essentials 的安全云存储和数据管理，实现供应链整合。通过基于权限的共享和无限制访客访问权限，您可以与团队成员、同事、合作伙伴和客户进行协作。安全的在线项目存储提供多用户覆盖保护、500 GB 基本存储空间以及可选的额外存储空间，所有这些都基于单一数据源运行。无论您的设计团队身在何处，都能在云端同步更改，实现实时更新和即时协作。
Translated: Implement supply chain integration by utilizing NX X Essentials secure cloud storage and data management. Through permission-based sharing and unrestricted access to access rights, you can collaborate with team members, colleagues, partners, and customers. Secure online project storage provides multi-user coverage protection, 500 GB of basic storage space, and optional additional storage space, all running on a single data source. No matter where your design team is, you can synchronize changes in the cloud, realizing real-time updates and instant collaboration.

Content: CAD 查看和批注功能适用于所有设备，支持在工程导向型三维空间中对模型进行查看、测量和批注。通过该功能，您可以对模型进行缩放、旋转或检查，并添加注释和评论。所有批注和评论在 NX X Essentials 中都完全可追溯并可随时查看，让项目审查全程可见。通过增强现实 (AR)，您可以使用智能设备在真实环境中预览设计效果。
Translated: CAD viewing and annotation functionality is applicable to all devices, supporting the viewing, measurement and annotation of models in engineering-oriented 3D space. Through this function, you can zoom, rotate or inspect the model, and add annotations and comments. All annotations and comments in NX X Essentials are fully traceable and can be viewed at any time, making the project review process fully visible. Through augmented reality (AR) in NX X Essentials, you can use smart devices to preview design effects in a real environment.

Content:
集成式 CAM 和仿真工具
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down
Translated:
Integrated CAM and simulation tools
arrow_drop_uparrow_drop_down

Content: NX X Essentials 制造功能可自动执行 2.5 轴 CAM 工序，包括面加工、腔加工、轮廓铣、开槽、钻孔、攻丝、倒斜角和镗孔。设置定制包括控制器选择、自定义刀具创建，以及刀具路径仿真，确保产品符合精确规格。
Translated: NX X Essentials manufacturing capabilities can automatically execute 2.5-axis CAM processes, including surface machining, cavity machining, contour milling, grooving, drilling, tapping, chamfering and countersinking. Custom settings include controller selection, custom tool creation, and toolpath simulation to ensure that the product meets precise specifications.
